--
-- SIGNALS CHECKED:
--  [5pts] BodyVelocity + BodyGyro TOGETHER in HRP  = fly script
--  [5pts] LinearVelocity + AlignOrientation TOGETHER = modern fly
--  [5pts] Known executor GUI name in PlayerGui
--  [5pts] LocalScript/Script injected inside character
